<div id="main">
<p id="results" style="clear:both">There are <strong id="straight">33.90</strong> miles from <strong>Stamford</strong> to <strong>New York</strong> in southwest direction<span id="resultsroad">
and <strong id="route">40</strong> miles (<span id="rkm">64.37 kilometers</span>) by car<span id="followingRoute">, following the I-95 S route</span>.</span></p>
<p id="time-result">Stamford and New York are <strong id="time"> 49 minutes</strong> far apart, if you drive non-stop .</p>
<p id="bestroute">This is the fastest <a href="https://howtogetfrom.com/route-from-stamford-ct-to-new-york-ny">route from Stamford, CT to New York, NY</a>.
<span id="halfway">The halfway point is Pelham, NY.</span></p>
<p>Stamford, CT and New York, NY are in the <strong>same time zone</strong> (EDT). Current time in both locations is 6:23 am.</p>
